latestIgtvVideos.title: Speak your mind out.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Small opportunities often open big doors! So, i had participated in an E- Media fest “Esperanza 2.0” conducted by @inspiria.tv 

The events organised had a creative edge which triggered me to participate in “speak your mind out/monologue” for which I won the First prize credentials. My motive was never to win. My motive of writing this was to let people hear, hear what i deeply felt & needed someone to speak out! Why not me then? 
Cant thank @inspiriaindia college for such a great opportunity. Sometimes its really good to be hard on ourselves!
.
.
.
#speakyourmindout #inspiriatv #w2lmotivation

Welcome to our very real, very messy shoot day!

One of us sets up the camera, the other sets up lunch.
One yells “Let’s shoot fast,” the other yells “Let’s eat first!”
One cleans… the other claims she’s “emotionally exhausted.”

But at the end of the day, we get the content (and the calories).
That’s sisterhood, right?
